<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.markboulton.co.uk/journal/comments/five_simple_steps_to_typesetting_on_the_web_the_right_glyph_for_the_job/">Mark Boulton: The Right Glyph for the Job</a> (ellipsis, quotes, ligatures)</li>
<li><a href="http://www.markboulton.co.uk/journal/comments/five_simple_steps_to_typesetting_on_the_web_dashes/">Mark Boulton: Dashes</a></li>
